    }
  ]} />

  <!-- Section 10: CTA -->
  <h2 id="next-steps">Ready to Explore Conventional Loans in San Diego?</h2>
  <p>
    A conventional loan gives you flexibility, the ability to drop PMI, and access to a wide range of property types. If you have solid credit and some savings, it can be the most cost-effective mortgage option over the long term. The next step is talking to a local lender who can compare conventional scenarios with FHA and other programs side by side.
  </p>
